00 +0000</pubDate><author>arbe.94@hotmail.com (Daniel Arbelaez Alvarez)</author><guid>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2026/01/08/por-que-transforme-este-espacio/</guid><description/></item><item><title>First Thoughts</title><link>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2025/06/14/thoughts/</link><pubDate>Sat, 14 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>arbe.94@hotmail.com (Daniel Arbelaez Alvarez)</author><guid>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2025/06/14/thoughts/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Escribir acerca de &lt;a href="https://keep.google.com/#LIST/1ai8F-_aBmcGHjUo2xUsLS2qlvN1OGOpgPBddBYzRLszUpEE5xPEzoOQYUmmP82DuHRZW">link directo&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote></description></item><item><title>El programador flanker: De la cancha de rugby a la arquitectura de software</title><link>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2025/02/28/design-pattern-in-public/</link><pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>arbe.94@hotmail.com (Daniel Arbelaez Alvarez)</author><guid>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2025/02/28/design-pattern-in-public/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Marduk: Un Viaje hacia la Innovación Judicial Digital</title><link>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2024/10/12/transformando-la-justicia/</link><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>arbe.94@hotmail.com (Daniel Arbelaez Alvarez)</author><guid>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2024/10/12/transformando-la-justicia/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Cola en un gestor de tareas</title><link>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2024/04/10/queue_example/</link><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>arbe.94@hotmail.com (Daniel Arbelaez Alvarez)</author><guid>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2024/04/10/queue_example/</guid><description>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">class&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#50fa7b">GestorTareas&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">def&lt;/span> __init__(self):
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Inicializamos la cola de trabajo como una lista vacía&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> self&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>cola_de_trabajo &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">=&lt;/span> []
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">def&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#50fa7b">agregar_tarea&lt;/span>(self, tarea):
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Añadimos la tarea al final de la cola de trabajo&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> self&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>cola_de_trabajo&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>append(tarea)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">def&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#50fa7b">procesar_siguiente_tarea&lt;/span>(self):
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Verificamos si hay tareas en la cola de trabajo&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">if&lt;/span> self&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>cola_de_trabajo:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Eliminamos y devolvemos la primera tarea de la cola&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">return&lt;/span> self&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>cola_de_trabajo&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>pop(&lt;span style="color:#bd93f9">0&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">else&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Si no hay tareas pendientes, devolvemos un mensaje indicándolo&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">return&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;No hay tareas pendientes&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">if&lt;/span> __name__ &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">==&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;__main__&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Ejemplo de uso del gestor de tareas&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> gestor &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">=&lt;/span> GestorTareas()
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Agregamos algunas tareas a la cola de trabajo&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> gestor&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>agregar_tarea(&lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;Revisar informe mensual&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> gestor&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>agregar_tarea(&lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;Enviar correo de seguimiento&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> gestor&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>agregar_tarea(&lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;Preparar presentación para reunión&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Procesamos y mostramos la tarea actual&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic">print&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;Tarea actual:&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, gestor&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>procesar_siguiente_tarea())
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Simulamos procesar algunas tareas adicionales&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic">print&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;Tarea actual:&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, gestor&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>procesar_siguiente_tarea())
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic">print&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;Tarea actual:&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, gestor&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>procesar_siguiente_tarea())
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Agregamos más tareas a la cola de trabajo&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> gestor&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>agregar_tarea(&lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;Resolver problema de software&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> gestor&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>agregar_tarea(&lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;Entrevistar candidato para puesto vacante&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Procesamos y mostramos la siguiente tarea&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic">print&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;Tarea actual:&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, gestor&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>procesar_siguiente_tarea())
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2024/04/10/stack_queue/">Volver&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Pila en un navegador web</title><link>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2024/04/10/stack_example/</link><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>arbe.94@hotmail.com (Daniel Arbelaez Alvarez)</author><guid>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2024/04/10/stack_example/</guid><description>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">class&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#50fa7b">NavegadorWeb&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">def&lt;/span> __init__(self):
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Inicializamos el historial como una lista vacía&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> self&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>historial &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">=&lt;/span> []
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">def&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#50fa7b">abrir_pagina&lt;/span>(self, url):
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Añadimos la URL al final del historial&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> self&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>historial&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>append(url)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">def&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#50fa7b">retroceder&lt;/span>(self):
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Verificamos si hay más de una página en el historial&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">if&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic">len&lt;/span>(self&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>historial) &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#bd93f9">1&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Retrocedemos eliminando la página actual del historial&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> self&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>historial&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>pop()
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Devolvemos la URL de la página anterior&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">return&lt;/span> self&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>historial[&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">-&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#bd93f9">1&lt;/span>]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">else&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Si no hay páginas anteriores, devolvemos un mensaje indicándolo&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">return&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;No hay páginas anteriores en el historial&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">def&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#50fa7b">adelantar&lt;/span>(self):
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Podríamos implementar la funcionalidad de avanzar utilizando otra pila para las páginas adelantadas&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">pass&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">if&lt;/span> __name__ &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">==&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;__main__&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Ejemplo de uso del navegador&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> navegador &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">=&lt;/span> NavegadorWeb()
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> navegador&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>abrir_pagina(&lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;https://www.ejemplo.com/pagina1&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> navegador&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>abrir_pagina(&lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;https://www.ejemplo.com/pagina2&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> navegador&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>abrir_pagina(&lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;https://www.ejemplo.com/pagina3&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Imprimimos la página actual&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic">print&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;Página actual:&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, navegador&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>historial[&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">-&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#bd93f9">1&lt;/span>])
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Retrocedemos una página y mostramos la página anterior&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> pagina_anterior &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">=&lt;/span> navegador&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>retroceder()
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic">print&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;Página anterior:&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, pagina_anterior)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#6272a4"># Retrocedemos otra página y mostramos la página anterior&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> pagina_anterior &lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">=&lt;/span> navegador&lt;span style="color:#ff79c6">.&lt;/span>retroceder()
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic">print&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#f1fa8c">&amp;#34;Página anterior:&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, pagina_anterior)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2024/04/10/stack_queue/">Volver&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Pilas y Colas: Estructuras de Datos Esenciales</title><link>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2024/04/10/stack_queue/</link><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>arbe.94@hotmail.com (Daniel Arbelaez Alvarez)</author><guid>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2024/04/10/stack_queue/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Explorando Delitos Informáticos y Riesgos Cibernéticos: Claves para la Seguridad Digital</title><link>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2023/08/15/delitos-informaticos-riesgos-ciberneticos/</link><pubDate>Tue, 15 Aug 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>arbe.94@hotmail.com (Daniel Arbelaez Alvarez)</author><guid>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2023/08/15/delitos-informaticos-riesgos-ciberneticos/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Una revisión del sistema experto Docassemble</title><link>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2023/07/11/docassemble-review/</link><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jul 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>arbe.94@hotmail.com (Daniel Arbelaez Alvarez)</author><guid>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2023/07/11/docassemble-review/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Optimiza la Gestión de tus Expedientes Electrónicos con GestiónExpedienteElectronico</title><link>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2022/12/01/gestion-expediente-electronico/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 Dec 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>arbe.94@hotmail.com (Daniel Arbelaez Alvarez)</author><guid>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2022/12/01/gestion-expediente-electronico/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Daniel Arbelaez (HammerDev99)</title><link>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2022/05/10/hello-world/</link><pubDate>Tue, 10 May 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>arbe.94@hotmail.com (Daniel Arbelaez Alvarez)</author><guid>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/2022/05/10/hello-world/</guid><description/></item><item><title/><link>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/about/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>arbe.94@hotmail.com (Daniel Arbelaez Alvarez)</author><guid>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/about/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="sobre-mí">Sobre mí&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Soy Daniel Arbelaez, ingeniero de software trabajando en el sistema judicial colombiano desde Bello, Antioquia.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Mi trabajo diario consiste en construir herramientas que hacen que la justicia funcione mejor. No desde la teoría, sino desde adentro: entendiendo cómo opera un juzgado, dónde se atoran los procesos, y cómo un buen algoritmo puede marcar la diferencia entre un expediente que avanza y uno que se pierde en el tiempo.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title/><link>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/notes/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>arbe.94@hotmail.com (Daniel Arbelaez Alvarez)</author><guid>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/notes/</guid><description/></item><item><title/><link>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/search/placeholder/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>arbe.94@hotmail.com (Daniel Arbelaez Alvarez)</author><guid>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/search/placeholder/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Posts Archive</title><link>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/archive/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>arbe.94@hotmail.com (Daniel Arbelaez Alvarez)</author><guid>https://blog.sprintjudicial.com/archive/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>